                    <li><a href="/blog/perbandingan-xpander-vs-xforce.html">Xpander vs XForce – Mana yang Lebih Cocok?</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/blog/kredit-mitsubishi-sleman.html">Tips Kredit Mitsubishi Sleman 2026</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Related -->
    <div class="related-strip">
        <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <h2 class="section-title">Unit Lain yang Menarik</h2>
            <div class="car-grid">
                <div class="car-card">
                    <img src="/images/xpander-cross.webp" alt="Xpander Cross Sleman" class="car-image" loading="lazy">
                    <div class="car-details">
